race.comment: CLARETOWN RAY (8) comes here after a scorching Grade 5 win at this track over 375m in 21.66. Can measure up again if runs up to latest time. DEL MAR BEEPER (4) finished in the money two on end before breaking through for an overdue win last start (21.86) at this track. Meets a moderate line up and should run well. SKEDADDLE PERCY (3) scored (21.93) last time out at this track in a Mix and will break from box 3 for the first time. Form here sound including two wins. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. UNACCEPTABLE AXE (2) found the frame for the second consecutive time when narrowly beaten into third last time out (23.73) over 400m at Mt Gambier.
